{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Summary — 完了 (かんりょう / done):**\n\nImplemented the help overlay for JEM-74:\n\n- **`src/views/help.rs`** — New view module rendering a centered popup listing all 16 keybindings (?, q, Ctrl+c, j/k, g/G, Enter, Esc, /, s, f, r, o, Tab, a) with yellow key labels and descriptions\n- **`src/app.rs`** — Added `show_help: bool` state field plus `toggle_help()` and `dismiss_help()` methods\n- **`src/main.rs`** — `?` toggles the overlay from any view; when shown, `Esc` or `?` dismisses it, blocking all other input\n- **Tests** — 10 new tests covering state toggling, dismiss idempotency, render safety (normal & small terminal), and keybinding content validation. All 126 tests pass, no new clippy warnings."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":494,"cache_read_input_tokens":78090,"output_tokens":235,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff78-9576-70cb-b385-66106a94285a"}
